Make the Ultimate Mental-Health Playlist
----------------------------------------

By Trudi Roth

Back in the day, a mixtape was the best way to capture what kids
today call #mood. Today we could all use some auditory uplift, as
COVID-related mental health conditions, including depression,
anxiety, and substance abuse, are skyrocketing (
https://click.convertkit-mail2.com/4zu7pwv4elhehvxkk7sx/n2hohqun8g5ezmt0/aH=
