WVudGFsLWhlYWx0aC1pc3N1ZXMtc2t5cm9ja2V0LWFzLXBhbmRlbWljLXdlYXJzLW9uLz9zaD02=
NGRhZGQ1MzY3NWQ=3D
).

Of course, data-driven Spotify knows this, reporting in October (
https://click.convertkit-mail2.com/4zu7pwv4elhehvxkk7sx/48hvh7u059qk4lhq/aH=
R0cHM6Ly93d3cuaW5kZXBlbmRlbnQuY28udWsvYXJ0cy1lbnRlcnRhaW5tZW50L211c2ljL25ld=
3Mvc3BvdGlmeS1tZW50YWwtaGVhbHRoLXBsYXlsaXN0LWNhbG0tbWluZGZ1bG5lc3MtcG9kY2Fz=
dC13b3JsZC1kYXktYjkwODEwOS5odG1s
) for World Mental Health Day that there=E2=80=99s been a 50% increase in
demand for mental-health-themed playlists, with 57% more searches
for =E2=80=9Cmindfulness,=E2=80=9D =E2=80=9Cself-care,=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=
=9Ccalm.=E2=80=9D And its year-end
=E2=80=9CWrapped (
https://click.convertkit-mail2.com/4zu7pwv4elhehvxkk7sx/wnh2h6ur54v8e6tl/aH=
R0cHM6Ly8yMDIwLmJ5c3BvdGlmeS5jb20vdXM_bG9jYWxlPXVz
)=E2=80=9D revealed a 180% jump in listening for health- and
wellness-related podcasts.

Still, the joy of the mixtape lies in making it yourself. With
all due respect, Spotify's algorithm put the ear-slicing anthem
=E2=80=9CStuck in the Middle With You=E2=80=9D from Reservoir Dogs (
