) violent music elicits aggressive thoughts and behavior.
* Got to choose: Curate your playlist according to your needs,
including grounding influences when you=E2=80=99re anxious or
mood-boosters when you=E2=80=99re down.
* Spirit of radio: Get your pod on with top-rated mental
